      "id": "gt-beat-kkr-match-25",
      "title": "GT blitz past KKR — Shubman Gill fires GT to 4th as Kolkata stay winless",
      "body": "Gujarat Titans chased 181 with 2 balls to spare at the Narendra Modi Stadium on April 17, powered by Shubman Gill's unbeaten half-century. The 5-wicket win lifts GT to 4th (6 points, NRR +0.018) in a bunched mid-table, while KKR slump to 0-5 from 6 games after Prasidh Krishna (11 wkts, new Purple Cap leader) struck early to restrict them to 180.",
      "tag": "On Fire"
